---
title: Apricot-Glazed Mumbai Diced Chicken with Sautéed Veggie Couscous & Yoghurt
description: Can’t decide between sweet or savoury, don’t worry we couldn’t either so we combined it into one! Tender diced chicken are cooked in our Mumbai spice blend and then tossed in a sticky-sweet apricot glaze. You won’t have to worry about picking one flavour over the other again with this recipe under your belt.

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving.*
